*** NOTE *** 
I have noticed a couple of quick dropouts in the 2nd set particularly during Ship of Fools and Stella Blue. I have checked this master copy and a backup I had going on another device and they are present both places. It seems it was an issue with the Sirius feed. I believe there are a couple other places where it sound like a "skip". This was also a problem with the Sirius feed, it sounds like dropped sample from the main satellite feed in general. This only happens a couple of times and is not terribly distracting. It was captured for archival purposes only but serves as a decent and perhaps the only Soundboard source we will see from any of the Garcia Symphony Celebration shows. Let's hope for an official release someday!
